{"tid":2056512,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（代貼）獅子銀行成日搵人笨 呃錢","createTime":"2020-06-08T17:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T11:36:44.000Z","uid":320858,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"18245d572dfcf1a8cc8aa6035fa2d91c80bf6d9e","tid":2056512,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:55:21.000Z","msg":"匯豐銀行成日呃人錢匯豐成日佔人便宜，十分仆街。<br />\n千萬不要用匯豐，不要用它仼何服務，不要用它信用卡,户口,尤其是樓宇按揭！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我之前匯豐青x城分行樓宇按揭供樓，職員態度差，騙我錢，死都不肯承認。之後要三番五次，要求高級主仼出來才肯承認。真超差！！！<br />\n<br />\n匯豐又難用又多野搞屎棍，尤其一堆行政費手續費，<br />\n啲Staff講嘢又差，好似唔熟啲細節。<br />\n<br />\n之前四年前都試過一次被匯豐騙錢。有一次在匯豐ATM 入數伍萬元正（從另一間銀行提款,銀碼已核對)。結果，ATM機顯示只有$49000。有 $1000不見，打去投訴，都不成功。個陣說要報警查清楚，查看CCTV 才願意退回$1000給我。"},{"pid":"6d3c2458b495ba297818e190126be544782671f3","tid":2056512,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:57:25.000Z","msg":"間間都係架啦"},{"pid":"4380c1d80611e8764a13a3ca01d62e5f886af0cb","tid":2056512,"uid":14152,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"d行文咁香討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8e8e9dad8c963e81def1e25d24b3ac2e518eda","tid":2056512,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"仆街獅子 以後唔撚用"},{"pid":"e5197d7ca709530b13b7080e5ce137f4847fa3ff","tid":2056512,"uid":1646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:09:29.000Z","msg":"睇完CCTV先比返你有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555ee6e99e46eb3fae4ff038a95407f67eff5f47","tid":2056512,"uid":167792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:14:20.000Z","msg":"mortgage 點呃法"},{"pid":"a7227b06f12b73c582f29b13bfd104801771d8c3","tid":2056512,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{